        <div class="guide__suggestion__number guide__suggestion__number--bottom">1.</div>
      </a>

      <h2 class="single__sub__header">Introduction</h2>
      <p>There are two podcasts.</p>
      <p><b>The NeverFap Deluxe Daily</b> which is the current podcast.</p>
      <p><b>The NeverFap Deluxe Podcast</b> which is the previous podcast.</p>
      <p>One is a daily motivation podcast, while the other is more of an in-depth discussion of various mental health topics. They're both quite different, but both are very useful. I recommend checking them both out.</p>
    </div>
